// Create Events Page elements
1. Calendar View (Group):
   - Install Calendar Plugin
   - Configure Calendar:
     - Data Source: Event
     - Date Field: Date
     - Title Field: Title

2. Event Details Panel (Group):
   - Visible when: Event is selected
   - Elements:
     - Title (Text)
     - Date (Text)
     - Description (Text)
     - Attendees Count (Number)
     - Register Button (Button):
       - Condition: Current User not in Event's Attendees

3. My Events Tab (Repeating Group):
   - Data Source: Current User's Registered_Events
   - Elements per cell:
     - Event Title (Text)
     - Date (Text)
     - Unregister Button (Button)